## ⏰ Time Complexity

```
O(n)

Where n = length of input string text

Reason:
→ We loop through text once to build freq map  → O(n)
→ We call min() on exactly 5 fixed values       → O(1)
→ Total = O(n) + O(1) = O(n)

Even if text has 1,000,000 characters
we still only loop once.
```

---

## 💾 Space Complexity

```
O(1)

Reason:
→ freq map stores at most 26 keys (a to z only)
→ 26 is a constant number
→ It does NOT grow as input grows
→ No extra arrays or lists used
→ Total = O(26) = O(1)
```

---

